{"tid":2359636,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律師會理事質疑政府棄約翰奈斯堡原則","createTime":"2021-01-09T05:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T06:11:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"edab713e76ecf28e57c48dd9f5fe4c9ee428db08","tid":2359636,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/MJHKEUGJPJE37PUG4NSIIE2VWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FMJHKEUGJPJE37PUG4NSIIE2VWU%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXf4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=0b03766a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FMJHKEUGJPJE37PUG4NSIIE2VWU%2F&h=c49926e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/MJHKEUGJPJE37PUG4NSIIE2VWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n律師會理事質疑政府棄約翰奈斯堡原則<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】 警方前日動用過千警力，全城大搜捕53名民主派人士，指他們涉透過「非法手段」達至「顛覆國家政權」，但連身兼行政會議成員的資深大律師湯家驊在內的法律界人士，也質疑初選屬「非法手段」的說法，湯坦言「到底初選違反咗咩法律？對唔住暫時我睇唔到」。包括帝理邁、林洋鋐、張達明、蔡頴德及黃耀初五名律師會理事發聲明，要求港府交代是否已放棄《約翰奈斯堡關於國家安全、言論自由和獲取信息自由原則》及《基本法》中，個人權利及自由保障的原則。<br />\n<br />\n警方前日被輪流追問，議員有權利否決財政預算案，而特首即使下台仍可補。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊於節目中表示，《基本法》第73條列明立法會職能包括審核和通過財政預算，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4NH_Af2uQfwpLMqeHgkRiTg06_c=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZQ3HDKCUPBAW5D3NOGDG4AGQ4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4NH_Af2uQfwpLMqeHgkRiTg06_c%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZQ3HDKCUPBAW5D3NOGDG4AGQ4A.jpg&h=e0c04e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯家驊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊：全心否決財案非刑事<br />\n<br />\n他重申要證明《國安法》第22條，必須有「以武力、威脅使用武力或者其他非法手段」三大元素，以及犯罪意圖，但至今警方未有解釋「非法行為」是指甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n港大法律學院首席講師張達明表示，根據普通法，除非明文禁止行為是非法，否則行為都不算非法，對有建制派曾聲言「《基本法》無授權初選，就係非法」，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n律師會五名理事包括帝理邁、林洋鋐、張達明、蔡頴德及黃耀初，昨以個人名義發。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zp3SnfQjwRCdZcLeEXT1Yk89WuE=/947x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5M6PHADM7RD7JCUU2KXWDV3F2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fzp3SnfQjwRCdZcLeEXT1Yk89WuE%3D%2F947x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5M6PHADM7RD7JCUU2KXWDV3F2I.jpg&h=7f5797cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚耀宗"},{"pid":"e8fe6c1e512113dd46422ddd5fc1c4ac940efe5b","tid":2359636,"uid":134087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"睇唔透律師會"},{"pid":"8add7de40c5b70e90682502965b08d41332938bd","tid":2359636,"uid":40520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e8fe6c1e512113dd46422ddd5fc1c4ac940efe5b","tid":2359636,"uid":134087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"睇唔透律師會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:55:04.000Z","msg":"睇透左大律師公會"},{"pid":"6ce946034e76abf93fedbd2f6746490b3b20c788","tid":2359636,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8fe6c1e512113dd46422ddd5fc1c4ac940efe5b","tid":2359636,"uid":134087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"睇唔透律師會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"依家係幾個民主派Law Soc理事私下出聲明 而個垃圾會長同其它咂奶共理事繼續扮盲唔肯用個會嘅名義出聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50e3103ac085ddd1365a01d22463a9160e9269c","tid":2359636,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:00:29.000Z","msg":"港共 : 係呀～我放棄左了 ,有咩問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e03482d5c692a79784b909b9602e99e55b20762","tid":2359636,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"提示插贓方向"},{"pid":"e27801e84fc67bc5de7b9616334bde2ffd7dfd65","tid":2359636,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c50e3103ac085ddd1365a01d22463a9160e9269c","tid":2359636,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:00:29.000Z","msg":"港共 : 係呀～我放棄左了 ,有咩問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:05:05.000Z","msg":"好快全世界都係我話事，理撚得你咩條約<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f690a25ed2ebd27a21df0fc3ad4a9ef3b2bf8fb","tid":2359636,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ce946034e76abf93fedbd2f6746490b3b20c788","tid":2359636,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8fe6c1e512113dd46422ddd5fc1c4ac940efe5b","tid":2359636,"uid":134087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"睇唔透律師會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"依家係幾個民主派Law Soc理事私下出聲明 而個垃圾會長同其它咂奶共理事繼續扮盲唔肯用個會嘅名義出聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:06:23.000Z","msg":"律師會官方聲明得呢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港律師會就終審法院首席法官馬道立榮休之聲明<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港律師會對終審法院首席法官馬道立，自 2010 年 9 月帶領香港司法機構，以及他對本會的支持，表達由衷謝意。<br />\n2. 近年有人意圖將一些法院工作政治化，這些意圖，在觀感上對作為法治核心價值的司法獨立，構成挑戰。<br />\n3. 馬道立首席法官捍衛法治和司法獨立不遺餘力，香港司法機構在他領導下，尤其於不少艱難時刻，仍維持穩固、獨立，受國際尊崇。<br />\n4. 引用馬道立首席法官的退休前法庭儀式致辭，香港律師會認為他領導司法機構絕對「可以說那美好的仗我已經打過了」。<br />\n5. 香港律師會衷心希望馬道立首席法官，在他的人生新一頁，事事順景美滿。<br />\n<br />\n香港律師會<br />\n2021 年 1 月 8 日"},{"pid":"e569426f92a10033a68d34b9e85b8743ab5ff9c6","tid":2359636,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:06:26.000Z","msg":"理事私下出聲明<br />\n都起碼好過大律師公會班老柴潛到落地核"},{"pid":"bda8edcd0114a60edad641b5444152bc11530130","tid":2359636,"uid":301952,